               <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US" source="Name">Communication Channel</xsd:documentation>
               <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US" source="Definition">The channel or manner in which a communication can be made with the contact, such as telephone or email.</xsd:documentation>
