               <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US" source="Name">Individual Returnable Asset Identification</xsd:documentation>
               <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US" source="Definition">The returnable asset identifier for an individual piece of returnable packaging.</xsd:documentation>
