         <xsd:enumeration value="48">
            <xsd:annotation>
               <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US" source="Name">FEDAS PCK</xsd:documentation>
               <xsd:documentation xml:lang="en-US" source="Definition">SGI-DHO (Sporting Goods
                  Industry Data Harmonization Organization) is representing the interests of the
                  different stakeholders of the sporting goods industry (retailers + brands). Its
                  main task is the development and harmonisation of codes, which can be used by the
